            <div class="thumbinner" style="width:202px;"><a href="//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Enigma.jpg?uselang=ru" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ae/Enigma.jpg/200px-Enigma.jpg" width="200" height="267" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ae/Enigma.jpg/300px-Enigma.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ae/Enigma.jpg/400px-Enigma.jpg 2x" data-file-width="450" data-file-height="600"></a>
